args: Whew! We finally made it to the legendary\ncastle of {player_name}.
Looks like my job's done, then.
I hope you achieve that dream of yours,\nfriend. Take care now!
Thank you again for the escort.
How good to see you again, Elisanne!
Did you travel all the way from Peng Lai\njust to see us?
Indeed. You all did so much for me,\nand I wanted to thank you in person.
How thoughtful. In that case, let me show\nyou into the castle. I know His Highness\nwill be delighted to see you.
It's been a while, Su Fang.\nI'm happy you came to see us.
The journey must have been exhausting.\nDid you come on your own?
I set out from Peng Lai on my own,\nbut, er...got lost on the way.
Ah. I'm sorry to hear that.
I should have known this would be too\ngreat a journey for one who has rarely\nset foot outside of his hometown.
Fortunately, I happened upon a kindly\ntraveler who showed me the way.
That's quite a stroke of luck.
Yes, I truly am a fortunate man.\nSomeone always seems to be\nthere for me when I need it most.
And while I owe all of your people a\ndebt of gratitude, I owe you most of all.
That's why I came here—to thank you.
I almost feel bad for the trouble.
Oh, please! The only one who's\nbeen troubled here is you.
After all you did for me, I felt I needed\nto thank you in a truly personal way.
Which is why I brought these\npryroblossoms.
Oh wow! Are you going to set them off\nright here at the castle?
That's right. I know it's not much\ncompared to what you did for me, but...
Absolutely. We don't ever get to see\nthis kind of thing here, after all.
I'm sure the others will be just as happy,\nso let's see what you've got!
V-very well! I'll show you the finest\ndisplay I've ever done!
Whoa. There are SO many people here.
'Course there are! Were ya expectin'\nanything different?
You have put on displays in front of\nlarger crowds than this, surely?
Well, yes—but those were all at home.\nIt's another thing entirely to create\na show for so many strangers.
But I can't let this chance pass me by.\nNot if I want to achieve my dream...
Now then! Let's get started.\nThree...two...one... Ignition!
There certainly was a good deal of\ncheering there. This pleases me.
A lot of the people here have never\nseen a pyroblossom before.
I imagine they found it awe-inspiring.
Yes, I suppose you're right—which means\nI simply cannot let this chance pass me by!
Please allow me to become one of your\ncompanions, {player_name}!
Right, yes. I suppose I should explain\nmy reasons for this request first.
You see, I've long wanted to set off my\npyroblossoms outside of Peng Lai.
My dream is to spread them across the\ncontinent so everyone can know of them.
I want this more than anything.
I'm glad to hear you say as much!\nEr, but that's where you come in.
I learned the hard way that my dream isn't\nsomething I can bring true on my own.\nI'm not used to traveling, for one thing.
True. You had a tough time even finding\nthis castle.
Indeed. But YOU intend to keep traveling\nthe world, do you not?
So if I accompany you, I can practice\nmy craft in every new town we find!
Now I see why you're asking to join us.\nWell, I'm happy to help. Welcome aboard.
Of course. Let's show the world how\nbeautiful your pyroblossoms are.
With your help, I'm going to light up\nthe night skies everywhere!
